verse.lines:
{lang-eng}I need no other argument,
I need no other plea;
It is enough that Jesus died,
And that He died for me.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}My faith has found a resting place,
Not in device nor creed;
I trust the Ever-living One,
His wounds for me shall plead.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Enough for me that Jesus saves,
This ends my fear and doubt;
A sinful soul I come to Him,
He’ll never cast me out.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}My great Physician heals the sick,
The lost He came to save;
For me His precious blood He shed,
For me His life He gave.{/lang-eng}
